%20Lord%20Ram%20-%20the%20grand%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20officially%20inaugurated%20today%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20religious%20figures%2C%20politicians%20and%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20witnesses%20the%20ceremony%20in%20the%20ancient%20city%2C%20here's%20a%20look%20back%20at%20how%20a%20500-year%20dispute%20culminated%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1528%3A%20Babri%20Masjid's%20Origin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beginning%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20movement%20lies%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201528%20by%20Mir%20Baqi%2C%20a%20commander%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Babur.%20The%20belief%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20decades%20of%20debate%20and%20clashes%20between%20two%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1751%3A%20A%20Maratha%20Claim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriter%20and%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20Balbir%20Punj%2C%20in%20his%20book%20'Tryst%20with%20Ayodhya%3A%20Decolonisation%20of%20India'%2C%20writes%20that%20the%20Marathas%20sought%20control%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20Kashi%2C%20and%20Mathura%2C%20effectively%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20several%20contentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1858%3A%20Nihang%20Sikhs'%20Demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201858%2C%20Nihang%20Sikhs%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20claim%20Babri%20Masjid%20as%20Lord%20Ram's%20birth%20place.%20This%20incident%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20struggle%20for%20control%20over%20the%20disputed%20site%2C%20foreshadowing%20conflicts%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20landmark%202019%20ruling%2C%20mentioned%20that%20Nihang%20Baba%20Fakir%20Singh%20Khalsa%2C%20along%20with%2025%20Nihang%20Sikhs%2C%20reportedly%20barged%20into%20the%20Mosque's%20premises%20and%20made%20a%20claim%20that%20the%20site%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20the%20historic%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1885%3A%20The%20First%20Legal%20Claim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghubar%20Das%2C%20a%20priest%20of%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhara%20filed%20the%20first%20legal%20suit%20in%201885%2C%20seeking%20permission%20to%20build%20a%20temple%20on%20the%20outer%20courtyard%20of%20the%20mosque.%20Though%20dismissed%2C%20it%20set%20a%20legal%20precedent%20and%20kept%20the%20dispute%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20the%20British%20administration%20in%20the%20city%20put%20a%20fence%20around%20the%20site%20marking%20separate%20areas%20of%20worship%20for%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20and%20it%20stood%20that%20way%20for%20nearly%2090%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1949%3A%20'Ram%20Lalla'%20Idols%20Inside%20Babri%20Masjid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20of%20December%2022%2C%201949%2C%20saw%20the%20placement%20of%20'Ram%20Lalla'%20idols%20inside%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20intensifying%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20around%20the%20site%20and%20leading%20to%20legal%20battles%20over%20its%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindus%20claimed%20that%20the%20idols%20%26quot%3Bappeared%26quot%3B%20inside%20the%20mosque.%20The%20property%20dispute%20went%20to%20court%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1950-1959%3A%20Legal%20Suits%20Multiply%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20decade%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20legal%20suits%2C%20with%20Nirmohi%20Akhara%20seeking%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20idols%20and%20the%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20seeking%20possession%20of%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20quagmire%20deepened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1986-1989%3A%20Babri%20Masjid%20Locks%20Opened%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20controversial%20move%2C%20in%201986%2C%20during%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi-led%20Congress%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20locks%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20were%20opened%2C%20allowing%20Hindus%20to%20worship%20inside.%20This%20decision%20further%20fueled%20tensions%20and%20became%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20set%20a%20deadline%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%201990%2C%20escalating%20the%20demands%20for%20a%20temple.%20This%20period%20also%20saw%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20Rath%20Yatra%20by%20BJP%20veteran%20LK%20Advani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20seismic%20shift%20as%20political%20leaders%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20VHP%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20mobilised%20support%20for%20the%20'liberation'%20of%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1990%3A%20Rath%20Yatra%20and%20Failed%20Demolition%20Attempt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20Mandal%20Commission's%20implementation%20and%20rising%20political%20tensions%2C%20L.K.%20Advani's%20Rath%20Yatra%20in%201990%20aimed%20to%20mobilize%20support%20for%20the%20temple.%20Despite%20a%20failed%20attempt%20to%20demolish%20the%20mosque%2C%20it%20marked%20a%20significant%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1992%3A%20The%20Infamous%20Demolition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%201992%20witnessed%20a%20climax%20-%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20Despite%20assurances%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20mosque%20was%20razed%20by%20Hindu%20activists.%20The%20cataclysmic%20event%20and%20the%20riots%20that%20followed%20changed%20Indian%20politics%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1993-1994%3A%20Post-Demolition%20Riots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid's%20demolition%2C%20communal%20riots%20erupted%20across%20India%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao-led%20Central%20government's%20acquisition%20of%20the%20disputed%20area%20was%20challenged%20by%20Dr%20Ismail%20Faruqui%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20in%201994.%20The%20judgment%20upheld%20the%20acquisition%2C%20further%20entrenching%20the%20state's%20involvement%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2002-2003%3A%20ASI's%20Excavation%20and%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20Hearing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20began%20hearing%20the%20title%20case%20in%202002%2C%20and%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20conducted%20excavations%2C%20claiming%20evidence%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20beneath%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20battle%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2009-10%3A%20Liberhan%20Report%20Submission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20399%20sittings%20over%2016%20years%2C%20the%20Liberhan%20Commission%20submitted%20its%20report%2C%20revealing%20intricate%20details%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20and%20implicating%20key%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Liberhan%20Commission%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20June%202009%20-%20naming%20LK%20Advani%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20-%20almost%2017%20years%20after%20it%20began%20its%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court's%202010%20verdict%20attempted%20to%20settle%20the%20dispute%20by%20dividing%20the%20land%20among%20Hindus%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhara.%20However%2C%20the%20decision%20faced%20appeals%20and%20further%20legal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2019%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20Historic%20Judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20judgment%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20awarded%20the%20entire%20disputed%20land%20to%20Hindus%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20allocated%20an%20alternate%20site%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2020%3A%20Ram%20Temple%20Foundation%20Stone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20a%20grand%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20the%20Babri%20masjid%20site%20on%20August%205%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20'Bhoomi%20Pujan'%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20bringing%20a%20semblance%20of%20closure%20to%20a%20protracted%20legal%20saga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2024%3A%20PM%20Modi%20Inaugurates%20The%20Ram%20Temple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20led%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20the%20newly-built%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705911540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdlj49g4_babri-masjid-ram-temple-split-_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-explained-from-1528-to-2024-a-500-year-timeline-of-ayodhya-ram-temple-4909652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%20400%20pillars%2C%2044%20doors%2C%20and%20a%20brand%20new%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20-%20the%20grand%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20officially%20inaugurated%20today%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20religious%20figures%2C%20politicians%20and%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20in%20attendance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-explained-from-1528-to-2024-a-500-year-timeline-of-ayodhya-ram-temple-4909652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ra