7046161.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFormer%20Pakistani%20cricketer%20Shoaib%20Malik%20shocked%20many%20by%20marrying%20actress%20Sana%20Javed%20in%20a%20surprise%20ceremony.%20Sania%20Mirza%20had%20previously%20obtained%20a%20divorce%20via%20'Khula.'%20The%20affair%20reportedly%20spanned%20three%20years%2C%20originating%20from%20a%20reality%20show.%20Despite%20family%20attempts%20at%20reconciliation%2C%20Shoaib%20Malik%20and%20Sania%20Mirza%20chose%20to%20divorce.%20The%20Malik%20family%20supported%20Mirza%2C%20evident%20in%20their%20absence%20at%20Malik's%20wedding%20to%20Sana%20Javed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpakistani-cricketer-shoaib-malik-and-sana-javed-were-in-a-relationship-for-nearly-3-years-reports%2Farticleshow%2F107046161.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Army%20Helicopters%20Shower%20Flowers%20On%20Ayodhya%20As%20Ram%20Temple%20'Aarti'%20Begins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArmy%20helicopters%20showered%20flowers%20on%20Ayodhya%20and%2030%20artists%20played%20different%20Indian%20musical%20instruments%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20premises%20as%20the%20Aarti%20ceremony%20began%20at%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20on%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemple%20authorities%20said%20all%20the%20guests%20have%20been%20given%20bells%20which%20they%20will%20ring%20as%20the%20Aarti%20ceremony%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030%20musicians%20who%20are%20performing%20will%20play%20their%20instruments%20in%20unison%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20participating%20in%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20of%20Shri%20Ramlalla%20in%20the%20newly%20built%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20at%2012%20noon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historic%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20is%20being%20attended%20by%20representatives%20of%20all%20major%20spiritual%20and%20religious%20sects%20of%20the%20country.%20People%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20including%20representatives%20of%20various%20tribal%20communities%20are%20attending%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20address%20this%20distinguished%20gathering%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20all%20the%20Shastriya%20protocols%2C%20the%20programme%20of%20Pran%20Pratistha%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20Abhijeet%20Muhurta%20in%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20there%20are%20Seven%20Adhivasas%20in%20Pran%20Pratistha%20ceremony%2C%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20Adhivasas%20are%20in%20practice.%20There%20will%20be%20121%20Acharyas%20conducting%20the%20rituals.%20Ganeshwar%20Shastri%20Dravid%20will%20be%20overseeing%2C%20coordinating%20and%20directing%20all%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20Anushthan%2C%20and%20the%20principal%20Acharya%20will%20be%20Lakshmikant%20Dixit%20of%20Kashi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPran%20Pratishtha%20will%20be%20conducted%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20Sarsanghchalak%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20Governor%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Anandiben%20Patel%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20U.P.%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20other%20dignitaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharyas%20of%20all%20schools%20of%20Bharatiya%20spiritualism%2C%20religion%2C%20sect%2C%20system%20of%20worship%2C%20tradition%2C%20Sants%20of%20more%20than%20150%20traditions%2C%20Mahamandaleshwars%2C%20Mandaleshwars%2C%20Shrimahants%2C%20Mahants%2C%20Nagas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20leading%20figures%20of%20more%20than%2050%20Adivasi%2C%20Girivasi%2C%20Tatavasi%2C%20Dwipavasi%20tribal%20traditions%2C%20will%20remain%20present%20to%20witness%20the%20Prana%20Pratistha%20ceremony%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Bhavya%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20the%20tribal%20traditions%20being%20represented%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20hills%2C%20forests%2C%20coastal%20belts%2C%20islands%2C%20etc.%2C%20is%20happening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traditions%20include%20Shaiva%2C%20Vaishnav%2C%20Shaakta%2C%20Ganapatya%2C%20Patya%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Bauddha%2C%20Jain%2C%20Dashnam%2C%20Shankar%2C%20Ramanand%2C%20Ramanuj%2C%20Nimbarka%2C%20Madhva%2C%20Vishnu%20Nami%2C%20Ramsanehi%2C%20Ghisapanth%2C%20Garibdasi%2C%20Gaudiya%2C%20Kabirpanthi%2C%20Valmiki%2C%20Shankardev%20(Assam)%2C%20Madhav%20Dev%2C%20ISKCON%2C%20Ramakrishna%20Mission%2C%20Chinmaya%20Mission%2C%20Bharat%20Sevashram%20Sangha%2C%20Gayatri%20Parivar%2C%20Anukul%20Chandra%2C%20Thakur%20Parampara%2C%20Mahima%20Samaj%20of%20Odisha%2C%20Akali%2C%20Nirankari%2C%20Namdhari%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Radhasoami%2C%20and%20Swaminarayan%2C%20Varkari%2C%20Veer%20Shaiva%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20programme%20in%20the%20Garbha-Griha%2C%20all%20the%20witnesses%20will%20have%20darshan%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnificent%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Mandir%20is%20constructed%20in%20traditional%20Nagara%20style.%20Its%20length%20(east-west)%20is%20380%20feet%3B%20width%20250%20feet%20and%20height%20is%20161%20feet%3B%20and%20is%20supported%20by%20a%20total%20of%20392%20pillars%20and%2044%20doors.%20The%20pillars%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20temple%20showcase%20intricately%20sculpted%20depictions%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20gods%2C%20and%20goddesses.%20In%20the%20main%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20at%20ground%20floor%2C%20the%20childhood%20form%20of%20Bhagwan%20Shri%20Ram%20(the%20idol%20of%20Shri%20Ramlalla)%20has%20been%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20entrance%20to%20the%20Mandir%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%2C%20which%20can%20be%20approached%20by%20ascending%2032%20stairs%20through%20the%20Singh%20Dwar.%20There%20are%20a%20total%20of%20five%20Mandaps