tent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EConsumption%20of%20meat%20could%20be%20a%20touchy%20subject.%20Vegetarians%20and%20those%20who%20eat%20meat%20never%20find%20a%20common%20ground.%20But%20amidst%20the%20debate%20around%20ethics%20of%20eating%20meat%2C%20there%20are%20some%20hard%20facts%20that%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%20And%20a%20vide%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20shows%20exactly%20that.%20According%20to%20the%20statistics%20shown%20in%20the%20clip%2C%20humans%20across%20the%20world%20consume%20billions%20of%20animals.%20As%20per%20an%20old%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstage.economist.com%2Fgraphic-detail%2F2011%2F07%2F27%2Fcounting-chickens%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20humans%20are%20outnumbered%20by%20farm%20animals%20-%20chickens%20(19%20billion)%2C%20cows%20(1.5%20billion)%2C%20sheep%20(1%20billion)%20and%20pigs%20(1%20billion).%20Though%20the%20number%20of%20these%20animals%20at%20any%20one%20time%20is%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20number%20of%20people%2C%20the%20figures%20are%20dwarfed%20by%20the%20number%20of%20animals%20we%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20viral%20video%2C%20chickens%20are%20on%20the%20top.%20The%20daily%20count%20is%20extremely%20large%20-%20205%20million%20chickens%20every%20day.%20To%20comprehend%20the%20scale%2C%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20to%20understand%20if%20the%20data%20is%20brought%20down%20to%20the%20average%20minute%3A%20More%20than%20140%2C000%20chickens%20are%20slaughtered%20every%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUnbeliavable!%20Total%20number%20of%20animals%20eaten%20by%20people%20globally%F0%9F%A7%90%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdB1TOklZAv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdB1TOklZAv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Tansu%20Yegen%20(%40TansuYegen)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTansuYegen%2Fstatus%2F1748967829406105778%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20animals%20on%20top%20are%20sardines%20(14%20billion%20every%20year)%2C%20shrimp%20(3%20billion%20every%20year)%2C%20duck%20(2.9%20billion)%20and%20goose%20(2.1%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstonishingly%2C%20two%20billion%20octopuses%20and%20100%20million%20sharks%20are%20eater%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%201.5%20billion%20pigs%20are%20killed%20to%20feed%20the%20growing%20appetite%20for%20pork%2C%20bacon%2C%20ham%20and%20sausages%20-%20a%20number%20that%20has%20tripled%20in%20the%20last%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20in%20its%20report%20that%20most%20of%20their%20demand%20has%20come%20from%20middle%20income%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20which%20became%20the%20world's%20biggest%20consumer%20of%20meat%20as%20its%20economy%20boomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2019%2F02%2Fchart-of-the-day-this-is-how-many-animals-we-eat-each-year%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWEF%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20consumption%20in%20Europe%20and%20North%20America%20has%20stabilised%2C%20even%20dropped%20in%20some%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20despite%20rapidly%20catching%20up%20with%20China%20in%20terms%20of%20population%2C%20still%20consumes%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20the%20world's%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staggering%20number%20of%20chickens%20is%20because%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20poultry%20has%20replaced%20pork%20at%20the%20dinner%20tables.%20From%20just%2012%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20share%20of%20chicken%2C%20duck%2C%20goose%2C%20turkey%20and%20fowl%20has%20increased%20to%20one-third%20of%20all%20the%20meat%20eaten%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20red%20meat%2C%20beef%2C%20has%20seen%20its%20global%20share%20nearly%20halve%20in%20the%20last%2050%20years%2C%20to%2022%20per%20cent%2C%20said%20the%20WEF%20report.%20But%20it%20still%20remains%20nearly%20five%20times%20more%20popular%20than%20lamb.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705905780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqc1qfido_meat-shop-generic-unsplash-1200_625x300_17_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmore-than-100-billion-animals-are-eaten-every-year-on-the-top-is-4909142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%2C%20despite%20rapidly%20catching%20up%20with%20China%20in%20terms%20of%20population%2C%20still%20consumes%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20the%20world's%20meat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmore-than-100-billion-animals-are-eaten-every-year-on-the-top-is-4909142%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmore-than-100-billion-animals-are-eaten-every-year-on-the-top-is-4909142%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmore-than-100-billion-animals-are-eaten-every-year-on-the-top-is-4909142%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Malayalam%20Actors%2C%20Directors%20Share%20Constitution%20Preamble%20on%20Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22121142%2F1595847102_image-0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20hours%20to%20go%20for%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%2022%2C%20several%20celebrities%20from%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20have%20taken%20to%20sharing%20images%20of%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20on%20their%20social%20media%20handles.%20The%20move%20is%20a%20reminder%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20day%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata