ulmination%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20campaign%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%2016th%20century%20mosque%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%94%20built%20in%201528%20by%20Mir%20Baqi%2C%20commander%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Babur%20%E2%80%94%20by%20kar%20sevaks%20belonging%20to%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20outfits%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%20The%20demolition%2C%20which%20happened%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20concerted%20Hindutva%20movement%2C%20resulted%20in%20communal%20riots%20over%20months%2C%20which%20led%20to%20over%202%2C000%20deaths.%20The%20Babri%20Masjid%20has%20been%20a%20contested%20site%20since%201885%20as%20religious%20leaders%20and%20Hindutva%20outfits%20considered%20it%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20or%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20fight%20ensued%20in%201950%20when%20Gopal%20Visharad%20Sharma%20approached%20the%20Faizabad%20district%20court%20for%20the%20right%20to%20worship%20idols%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20which%20were%20placed%20there%20in%201949.%20On%20September%2030%2C%202010%2C%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20in%20a%202%3A1%20majority%2C%20ruled%20a%20three-way%20division%20of%20the%20disputed%20area%20between%20the%20Sunni%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhara%2C%20and%20Ram%20Lalla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20the%20entire%202.77%20acres%20of%20disputed%20land%20to%20deity%20Ram%20Lalla%20and%20directed%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20allot%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20Muslims%20for%20building%20a%20mosque.%20Though%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20referred%20to%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20demolition%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20egregious%20violation%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20verdict%20was%20criticised%20for%20accepting%20the%20logic%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfaith%20over%20fact%E2%80%9D%20and%20granting%20legal%20possession%20of%20land%20to%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5