3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705905000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107035625%2Cimgsize-65666.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fathiya-shettys-gorgeous-white-floral-ensemble-is-perfect-for-wedding-cocktails%2Fphotostory%2F107035625.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107035625.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAthiya%20Shetty%20sets%20ethnic%20fashion%20goals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fathiya-shettys-gorgeous-white-floral-ensemble-is-perfect-for-wedding-cocktails%2Fphotostory%2F107035625.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Creating%20A%20Ram%20Rajya%20-%20by%20Sadhguru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20tremendous%20excitement%20in%20the%20country%20about%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20because%20people%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20over%20500%20years.%20The%20process%20of%20consecrating%20a%20deity%20is%20about%20stabilizing%20an%20energetic%20or%20%3Cem%3Epranic%3C%2Fem%3E%20form%20that%20exudes%20certain%20qualities.%20The%20qualities%20that%20we%20ascribe%20to%20the%20deity%20are%20the%20same%20qualities%20that%20we%20hold%20high%20and%20aspire%20to.%20In%20this%20civilization%20that%20we%20refer%20to%20as%20Hindustan%2C%20we%20do%20not%20wait%20for%20divinity%20to%20descend%20but%20nurture%20and%20cultivate%20that%20possibility%20within%20us.%20In%20this%20effort%2C%20creating%20a%20stable%20base%20within%20is%20vital%2C%20and%20that%20is%20called%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Banushthanam%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Sanskrit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20effort%20to%20build%20a%20foundation%20of%20the%20divine%20possibility%20within%20ourselves.%20It%20is%20about%20turning%20this%20body%20into%20a%20living%20temple%20with%20purificatory%20processes%20and%20life-enhancing%20methods%2C%20making%20the%20body%20fit%20enough%20to%20house%20the%20divine.%20For%20all%20consecrations%20that%20we%20do%20at%20Isha%2C%20there%20is%20always%20an%20appropriate%20Yoga%20%3Cem%3Esadhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20participants.%20%3Cem%3EAnushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20done%20for%20various%20periods.%20There%20are%20%3Cem%3Esadhakas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewho%20do%20it%20for%20an%20entire%20solar%20cycle%2C%20which%20is%20just%20short%20of%2012%20years.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20done%20for%2036%20months%2C%20or%20for%2090%2C%2064%2C%2033%2C%2028%2C%2021%2C%2012%2C%2011%2C%209%2C%207%2C%205%20or%203%20days%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20type%20of%20%3Cem%3Eprana%20pratishtha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20%3Cem%3Esadhanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20designed%20to%20enable%20the%20participant%20to%20create%20a%20stable%20base%20within%20and%20to%20take%20the%20imprint%20of%20both%20the%20form%20and%20the%20qualities%20of%20the%20deity%20upon%20their%20Pranamaya%20Kosha%20and%20Vijnanamaya%20Kosha%2C%20which%20are%20beyond%20the%20physical%20body%20and%20mental%20structures.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Esadhanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20help%20store%20or%20sow%20the%20divine%20possibility%20into%20a%20deeper%20space%20within%20oneself%2C%20where%20the%20general%20rigor%20of%20life%20cannot%20deny%20or%20contaminate%20that%20possibility.%20In%20one's%20search%20for%20liberation%20or%20moksha%2C%20this%20is%20an%20important%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20relevant%20at%20the%20time%20of%20consecration%20but%20can%20be%20done%20at%20any%20time%20as%20convenient%20for%20people.%20It%20was%20a%20common%20practice%20for%20individuals%20endeavouring%20to%20take%20up%20significant%20activity%20in%20their%20lives%20to%20go%20into%20periods%20of%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20well-documented%20that%20kings%20performed%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20before%20venturing%20into%20war%20or%20important%20campaigns%20because%20success%20does%20not%20come%20due%20to%20one's%20desire%20but%20by%20ensuring%20that%20one's%20own%3Cem%3E%20pravritti%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20set%20patterns%20of%20function%2C%20do%20not%20become%20an%20impediment.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20take%20on%20any%20great%20challenges%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20to%20ensure%20is%20that%20you%20are%20not%20the%20problem.%20%3Cem%3EAnushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20powerful%20way%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20involves%20various%20methods%20per%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20individual.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20for%20every%20type%20of%20human%20being%2C%20a%20specific%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20be%20worked%20out.%20It%20can%20be%20prescribed%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%2C%20breath-related%2C%20ritualistic%2C%20energetic%2C%20or%20very%20consciousness-oriented%20processes.%20Every%20human%20being%20needs%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20doing%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20they%20want%20to%20live%20a%20life%20of%20impact%20and%20fulfilment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20very%20heartening%20to%20see%20that%20the%20elected%20leader%20of%20Bharat%20-%20this%20great%20crucible%20of%20civilization%20-%20is%20doing%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20upon%20Rama%2C%20who%20is%20held%20as%20the%20epitome%20of%20a%20just%2C%20stable%2C%20and%20prosperous%20ruler.%20Not%20just%20one%20leader%20but%20all%20leaders%20and%20citizens%20of%20Bharat%20should%20do%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20create%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%20or%20a%20nation%20that%20is%20based%20on%20principles%20and%20rules%2C%20which%20we%20refer%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bdharma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDharma%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20word%20has%20been%20confiscated%20by%20the%20common%20narrative%20of%20being%20a%20religion.%20Dharma%20means%20law.%20There%20were%20various%20types%20of%20dharmas%20-%20Rajadharma%20for%20the%20Raja%20(ruler)%2C%20Grihasta%20dharma%20for%20people%20in%20families%2C%20Guru%20dharma%20for%20teachers%20and%20various%20other%20dharmas%20for%20different%20kinds%20of%20activity.%20Dharma%20means%20rules%2C%20principles%20and%20ethics%20as%20to%20how%20one%20should%20function%20in%20a%20given%20position.%20But%20the%20most%20important%20dharma%20is%20svadharma%2C%20the%20dharma%20concerned%20with%20oneself%2C%20which%20is%20a%20spiritual%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20Ram%20Rajya%20mean%3F%20Is%20it%20about%20going%20back%20to%20bow-and-arrow%20times%3F%20No%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20fundamental%20ethics%20that%20one%20should%20hold%20when%20other%20people%20come%20under%20your%20influence.%20Leaders%20who%20keep%20their%20personal%20wellbeing%20aside%20for%20people's%20welfare%2C%20%3Cem%3Ethis%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Ram.%20Willing%20to%20sacrifice%20personal%20goals%20for%20the%20larger%20good%2C%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Ram.%20Addressing%20all%20negativity%20with%20equanimity%20and%20grace%2C%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Ram.%20Establishing%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20or%20dharma%2C%20no%20matter%20at%20what%20cost%2C%3Cem%3E%20that%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Ram.%20A%20constant%20striving%20to%20improve%20oneself%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20serve%20better%20every%20moment%20of%20your%20life%2C%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Ram.%20If%20leaders%20aspire%20to%20become%20this%20and%20do%20%3Cem%3Eanushthanam%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20these%20qualities%2C%20there%20shall%20be%20Ram%20Rajya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20say%20leaders%2C%20don't%20just%20think%20about%20political%2C%20military%20or%20business%20leaders.%20Leadership%20means%20you%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20another%20life%20-%20whether%20it%20is%20one%20or%20one%20billion%20lives.%20If%20you%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20influence%20and%20be%20a%20power%20upon%20another%20life%2C%20you%20must%20follow%20these%20five%20principles%20and%20create%20Ram%20Rajya%20wherever%20you%20are.%20Let%20us%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERanked%20amongst%20the%20fifty%20most%20influential%20people%20in%20India%2C%20Sadhguru%20is%20a%20Yogi%2C%20mystic%2C%20visionary%20and%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20bestselling%20author.%20Sadhguru%20has%20been%20conferred%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%202017%2C%20the%20highest%20annual%20civilian%20award%2C%20accorded%20for%20exceptional%20and%20distinguished%20service.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20people's%20movement%2C%20Conscious%20Planet%20-%20Save%20Soil%2C%20which%20has%20touched%20over%204%20billion%20people.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705904940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Flscvr3bs_sadhguru-1200_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcreating-a-ram-rajya-by-sadhguru-4908949%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20tremendous%20excitement%20in%20the%20country%20about%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20because%20people%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20over%20500%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcreating-a-ram-rajya-by-sadhguru-4908949%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcreating-a-ram-rajya-by-sadhguru-4908949%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcreating-a-ram-rajya-by-sadhguru-4908949%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20Clampdown%20Impacts%20Hospitality%20Workers%2C%20Including%20Indians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESince%20Brexit%20made%20it%20harder%20for%20Europeans%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20British%20pubs%20and%20restaurants%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20labor%20from%20further-flung%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20Now%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20planned%20crackdown%20on%20migration%20is%20threatening%20to%20stifle%20that%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArrivals%20to%20the%20UK%20from%20countries%20such%20as%20Nigeria%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20risen%20sharply%2C%20more%20than%20offsetting%20the%20number%20of%20departing%20EU%20citizens%2C%20and%20pushing%20overall%20levels%20of%20net%20migration%20to%20an%20all-time%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20there%20are%20less%20Europeans%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20more%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20people%20come%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alasdair%20Murdoch%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Burger%20King%20in%20the%20UK.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20Europeans%20went%20home%20during%20Covid%20and%20they%20didn't%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecord%20migration%2C%20despite%20the%20supply-side%20benefits%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20political%20storm%20after%20pro-Brexit%20campaigners%20promised%20to%20control%20the%20country's%20borders.%20Sunak%20is%20gambling%20on%20the%20Conservatives'%20controversial%20plan%20to%20send%20asylum%20seekers%20to%20Rwanda%2C%20while%20stamping%20down%20on%20economic%20migration%20with%20new%20limits%20on%20students%20and%20the%20families%20of%20people%20who%20are%20granted%20work%20visas.%20Yet%20these%20are%20the%20groups%20who%20often%20fill%20hospitality%20jobs%2C%20as%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20to%20work%20in%20a%20bar%20or%20eatery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkqpsg58c_eu-migration-graphic_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tend%20to%20employ%20more%20people%20doing%20fewer%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Burger%20King%20boss%20Murdoch%2C%20due%20to%20higher%20labor%20costs.%20He%20explained%20that%20many%20of%20his%20staff%20from%20outside%20Europe%20are%20students%20and%20so%20are%20well-suited%20to%20these%20jobs..%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20shift%20to%20more%20part-time%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospitality%20sector%20has%20already%20endured%20one%20of%20its%20toughest%20ever%20periods%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20a%20generational%20inflation%20crisis.%20Relentless%20train%20strikes%20and%20the%20lasting%20trend%20of%20remote%20working%20have%20also%20kept%20customers%20away%20from%20city%20and%20town%20centers%2C%20while%20bosses%20are%20now%20facing%20higher%20taxes%20and%20another%20sharp%20uplift%20in%20the%20minimum%20wage.%20A%20restriction%20on%20labor%20would%20add%20to%20the%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20103%2C000%20EU%20workers%20left%20the%20UK's%20accommodation%20and%20food%20services%20sector%20between%20December%202019%20-%20shortly%20before%20Brexit%20ended%20freedom%20of%20movement%20from%20the%20EU%20-%20and%20December%202022%2C%20according%20to%20net%20payroll%20data%20from%20HM%20Revenue%20%26amp%3B%20Customs.%20Over%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20number%20of%20other%20overseas%20staff%20grew%20by%2096%2C900.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdig1mi6g_eu-workers-graphic_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProposed%20changes%20to%20the%20migration%20system%20%26quot%3Bwill%20reduce%20the%20pool%20of%20migrant%20labor%20that%20businesses%20can%20hire%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ben%20Brindle%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20Migration%20Observatory%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford.%20In%20early%20December%2C%20Sunak%20vowed%20to%20increase%20the%20minimum%20salary%20needed%20to%20secure%20a%20skilled%20work%20visa%20by%20a%20third%2C%20to%2038%2C700%20pounds%20(%2449%2C000)%20-%20well%20above%20the%20average%20pay%20of%20most%20hospitality%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMigration%20isn't%20the%20only%20way%20to%20fill%20vacancies%2C%20so%20what%20happens%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20businesses%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20Brindle%20added.%20%26quot%3BIn%20theory%20they%20could%20improve%20pay%20to%20attract%20domestic%20workers%20or%20automate%20production%2C%20but%20in%20some%20cases%20these%20options%20won't%20be%20feasible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20business%20owners%20are%20concerned%20that%20British%20people%20won't%20apply%20for%20these%20types%20of%20jobs%2C%20if%20the%20supply%20of%20overseas%20workers%20is%20limited.%20Fears%20spread%20down%20the%20chain%20to%20suppliers%20of%20restaurants%20and%20pubs.%20%26quot%3BFor%20plants%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%2C%20in%20places%20where%20they%20just%20can't%20recruit%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nick%20Allen%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20British%20Meat%20Processors%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20faced%20with%20the%20decision%3A%20you%20incur%20huge%20extra%20cost%20or%20actually%20you%20tailor%20your%20business%20down%2C%20to%20fit%20the%20workers%20that%20you%20can%20get%20hold%20of.%20It%20could%20have%20some%20quite%20dramatic%20effects%2C%20and%20what%20the%20government%20should%20understand%20is%20whichever%20way%20that%20goes%20is%20going%20to%20create%20inflation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20spells%20a%20headache%20for%20Sunak%2C%20who%20has%20said%20a%20general%20election%20is%20likely%20in%20late%202024%20but%20is%20far%20behind%20the%20opposition%20Labour%20Party%20in%20polls.%20Inflation%20is%20still%20double%20the%202%25%20target%2C%20and%20Bank%20of%20England%20policymakers%20are%20worried%20that%20a%20tight%20labor%20market%20and%20rising%20wages%20are%20boosting%20domestic%20prices.%20Limiting%20the%20labor%20supply%20could%20be%20risky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllen%2C%20whose%20industry%20has%20been%20hit%20particularly%20hard%20by%20a%20lack%20of%20UK%20workers%2C%20said%20it%20was%20unrealistic%20to%20assume%20businesses%20could%20pay%20British%20people%20more.%20Due%20to%20the%20specialist%20skills%20required%2C%20many%20meat%20processing%20plants%20have%20been%20able%20to%20recruit%20workers%20from%20abroad%20under%20the%20UK's%20%26quot%3Bskilled%20worker%26quot%3B%20program.%20The%20Philippines%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20hunting%20ground%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20expensive.%20Allen%20reckons%20the%20cost%20of%20recruiting%20and%20hiring%20Filipino%20workers%20-%20paying%20for%20their%20visas%2C%20travel%20and%20so%20on%20-%20averages%20out%20to%205%2C000%20pounds%20per%20year%20over%20the%20length%20of%20their%20employment.%20That's%20over%20the%20domestic%20rate%20of%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20would%20not%20be%20doing%20it%20if%20it%20was%20just%20a%20simple%20matter%20of%20offering%20higher%20wages%20-%20you%20just%20cannot%20find%20the%20people%20to%20do%20the%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Allen%20said.%20The%20new%20minimum%20salary%20for%20migrant%20workers%20of%2038%2C700%20pounds%20is%20far%20higher%20than%20the%20going%20rate%2C%20Allen%20added%2C%20leaving%20many%20executives%20in%20the%20meat%20industry%20scratching%20their%20heads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20and%20Drink%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20will%20be%20felt%20across%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20food%20industry.%20In%20December%202020%2C%2067%25%20of%20staff%20at%20one%20large%20casual%20dining%20chain%20were%20British%2C%2016%25%20were%20from%20the%20EU%20and%2011%25%20were%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20(the%20remainder%20were%20unspecified).%20By%20December%202022%2C%20the%20rest-of-world%20proportion%20had%20risen%20to%2019%25%2C%20while%20the%20EU%20share%20had%20dipped%20to%209%25.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIan%20Cass%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Forum%20of%20British%20Pubs%2C%20said%20there%20were%20fewer%20EU%20staff%20employed%20in%20bars%20across%20the%20UK%20since%20Brexit%2C%20and%20their%20departure%20was%20being%20felt%20most%20keenly%20in%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritons%20haven't%20been%20rushing%20in%20to%20fill%20the%20gaps%2C%20he%20added.%20Although%20demand%20for%20staff%20is%20high%2C%20it%20varies%20greatly%20by%20locality%20and%20changing%20drinking%20habits%20mean%20many%20pubs%20are%20closing%20earlier%20than%20in%20the%20past.%20%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20need%20workers%20on%20less%20hours%2C%20and%20they're%20making%20less%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Cass%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20also%20has%20proven%20a%20difficulty%20to%20getting%20people%20into%20the%20hospitality%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20pubs%2C%20he%20added%2C%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20pay%20staff%20more.%20Cass%20called%20for%20immigration%20restrictions%20to%20be%20loosened%20on%20catering%20staff%20looking%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20if%20only%20during%20busy%20periods%20over%20the%20summer.%20%26quot%3BThey%20ain't%20going%20to%20be%20making%20a%2030-pounds-odd-grand%20salary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospitality%20industry%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20working%20hard%20to%20make%20itself%20a%20more%20attractive%20one%20for%20people%20to%20join%2C%20with%20salaries%20up%2013%25%20on%20average%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kate%20Nicholls%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20trade%20body%20UKHospitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPopulation%20Growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20lecture%20hosted%20by%20conservative%20think-tank%20Bright%20Blue%2C%20Alan%20Manning%2C%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20said%20it%20was%20right%20to%20reduce%20net%20migration.%20Current%20levels%20had%20put%20the%20UK's%20population%20growth%20on%20an%20unsustainable%20trajectory%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20hiring%20workers%20who%20were%20in%20shortage%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20increase%20salaries%2C%20he%20added%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20allowed%20to%20import%20staff%20on%20lower%20wages%20-%20though%20he%20said%20the%20salary%20threshold%20for%20migrants%20of%2038%2C700%20pounds%20was%20too%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ft7l0c08c_sunak-graphic_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20ask%20more%20often%20than%20we%20do%20why%20we%20have%20shortages%2C%26quot%3B%20Manning%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlmost%20always%2C%20when%20we%20get%20into%20the%20lower-paid%2C%20lower-skilled%20jobs%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20shortages%20is%20not%20that%20we're%20short%20of%20people%20who%20are%20able%20to%20do%20these%20jobs.%20We're%20short%20of%20people%20in%20the%20local%20economy%20who%20want%20to%20do%20these%20jobs.%20That's%20because%20of%20poor%20pay%20and%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sentiment%20is%20not%20always%20shared%20by%20business%20leaders.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20government%20doesn't%20take%20into%20account%20is%2C%20once%20you%20bring%20people%20in%20at%20that%2038%2C700%20pounds%20rate%2C%20everyone%20around%20them%20will%20want%20and%20expect%20to%20be%20paid%20the%20same%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20Allen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20seems%20to%20announce%20these%20things%20and%20quite%20frankly%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20they're%20making%20it%20up%20as%20they%20go%20along.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705904820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Futu36qns_rishi-sunak_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-rishi-sunak-clampdown-impacts-hospitality-workers-including-indians-4909054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20Brexit%20made%20it%20harder%20for%20Europeans%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20British%20pubs%20and%20restaurants%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20labor%20from%20further-flung%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20Now%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20planned%20crackdown%20on%20migration%20is%20threatening%20to%20stifle%20that%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-rishi-sunak-clampdown-impacts-hospitality-workers-including-indians-4909054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-rishi-sunak-clampdown-impacts-hospitality-workers-including-indians-4909054%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-rishi-sunak-clampdown-impacts-hospitality-workers-including-indians-4909054%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshayakalpa%20Organic%20announces%20new%2C%20modern%20dairy%20facility%20near%20Chennai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705904814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F22%2Ffull%2F1705904143-7998.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakshayakalpa-organic-announces-new-modern-dairy