ed%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%2C%20which%20claimed%20no%20restriction%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20temples%20to%20live%20stream%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20event.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20the%20state%20government%20to%20consider%20applications%2C%20if%20any%2C%20for%20telecasting%20the%20pran%20prathistha%20ceremony%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20had%20removed%20some%20LED%20screens%20set%20up%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20at%20public%20places%20over%20allegations%20that%20they%20did%20not%20take%20permission%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20asking%20for%20permission%20to%20allow%20live%20stream%20from%20Ayodhya%20in%20LED%20screens%20installed%20across%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20her%20posts%20from%20yesterday%2C%20when%20she%20pointed%20out%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20over%20200%20temples%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20the%20police%20have%20been%20stopping%20even%20private%20temples%20from%20live%20streaming%20the%20pran%20prathistha%20ceremony%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20today%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20repression%20saga%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20continues%3A%20a%20small%20village%20(not%20more%20than%20200%20houses)%20where%20people%20wanted%20to%20celebrate%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20mandir%20and%20watch%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20participate%20have%20been%20told%20that%20unless%20the%20district%20collector%20(DC)%20gives%20permission%2C%20they%20shall%20not%20install%20the%20hired%20LED%20screen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DC%20is%20sitting%20on%20the%20matter.%20LED%20supplier%20is%20threatened.%20Village%3A%20Karunilam%20district%2C%20Chengalpattu%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%20government%20under%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20refuted%20her%20allegations%2C%20saying%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%2