they%20will%20rip%20off%20pandals.%20Strongly%20condemn%20this%20anti-Hindu%2C%20hateful%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20month%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20had%20drawn%20ire%20from%20her%20state%20counterpart%20for%20%E2%80%9Carrogance%E2%80%9D.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20finance%20minister%20Thangam%20Thennarasu%20said%20on%20December%2023%2C%202023%20that%20Sitharaman%20had%20insulted%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20by%20indicating%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Carrogant%E2%80%9D%20language%20that%20the%20Centre%20would%20not%20meet%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20twin%20demands%20of%20declaring%20the%20recent%20floods%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98calamity%20of%20severe%20nature%E2%80%99%20and%20allocating%20additional%20funds%20of%20Rs%2021%2C692%20crore%20towards%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20her%20comments%2C%20made%20at%20a%20media%20interaction%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20said%20Sitharaman%20had%20only%20exposed%20her%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20compassion%E2%80%9D%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu%20by%20thinking%20that%20she%20was%20being%20critical%20of%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin.%20He%20clarified%20that%20the%20state%20had%20not%20requested%20the%20Centre%20to%20declare%20the%20floods%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20disaster%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccalamity%20of%20a%20severe%20nature%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fnirmala-sitharaman-has-insulted-the-people-of-tamil-nadu-thangam-thennarasu%2Farticle67666895.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20morning%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20heard%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20members%20seeking%20permission%20to%20live%20stream%20the%20pran%20patishtha%20ceremony%20on%20LED%20screens.%20The%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1749299916252299507%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20court%20in%20response%3C%2Fa