an-chatgpt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDean.Bot%20conversed%20with%20constituents%20in%20real%20time%20while%20mimicking%20the%20long%20shot%20Democratic%20challenger%20for%20president%2C%20using%20an%20AI-generated%20version%20of%20Phillips'%20voice%20to%20respond%20to%20user%20questions%2C%20like%20why%20Democrats%20shouldn't%20be%20throwing%20their%20weight%20behind%20incumbent%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20respect%20President%20Biden%2C%20the%20data%20and%20conversations%20with%20Americans%20across%20the%20country%20indicates%20a%20strong%20desire%20for%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20WaPo%20reported%20Dean.Bot%20responded%20in%20an%20AI-generated%20voice%20that%20sounded%20like%20Phillips'%20but%20had%20an%20unusual%20cadence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillips'%20background%20is%20in%20business.%20He%20ran%20his%20family's%20distilling%20company%20between%202000%20and%202012%20before%20pivoting%20to%20run%20Talenti%2C%20the%20popular%20gelato%20company%20he'd%20invested%20in%20until%20it%20was%20sold%20in%202014.%20He%20has%20represented%20Minnesota%20since%202019%20and%20launched%20his%20campaign%20to%20challenge%20Biden%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20his%20polling%20numbers%20haven't%20indicated%20he'd%20be%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20creation%20of%20Dean.Bot%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20Super%20PAC%20We%20Deserve%20Better%2C%20WaPo%20reported.%20The%20PAC%20then%20partnered%20with%20AI%20developer%20Delphi%20to%20build%20the%20bot.%20Delphi's%20account%20was%20suspended%20for%20violating%20the%20political%20rules%20late%20Friday%2C%20just%20a%20day%20after%20WaPo%20wrote%20about%20the%20creation%20of%20Dean.Bot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20earlier%20this%20month%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fblog%2Fhow-openai-is-approaching-2024-worldwide-elections%5C%22%20target%