nsider.com%2F65a779f943bb77284b9d9ac3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJia%20Hui%20Ong%2C%2026%2C%20served%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%20for%20five%20years%20before%20she%20made%20the%20transition%20to%20the%20private%20sector.%3Cp%3EJia%20Hui%20Ong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJia%20Hui%20Ong%20enlisted%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%20when%20she%20was%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOng%2C%2026%2C%20served%20for%20five%20years%20before%20she%20left%20for%20the%20private%20sector.%20She%20is%20now%20on%20a%20career%20break.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOng%20said%20that%20serving%20in%20the%20army%20helped%20develop%20her%20sense%20of%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fjiahuiongggg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJia%20Hui%20Ong%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20who%20left%20the%20military%20to%20join%20the%20private%20sector.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20quite%20directionless%20as%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20I%20was%20filled%20with%20self-doubt.%20I%20was%20always%20questioning%20my%20own%20decisions%20and%20doubting%20my%20self-worth.%20I%20briefly%20considered%20going%20to%20college%20but%20felt%20I%20wasn't%20academically%20inclined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remembered%20how%20my%20father%20would%20tell%20me%20about%20his%20days%20as%20a%20commando%20and%20the%20exciting%20things%20he'd%20do%2C%20like%20jumping%20out%20of%20a%20helicopter.%20He%20also%20told%20me%20that%20the%20military%20helped%20define%20his%20life%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20that%20for%20myself%2C%20too.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20enlist%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%20(SAF)%20instead%20of%20pursuing%20a%20college%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20dad%20was%20very%20supportive%20of%20my%20decision%2C%20my%20mum%20was%20initially%20a%20bit%20skeptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20male%20friends%20also%20questioned%20my%20decision.%20They%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20go%20through%20this%3F%20Females%20can%20do%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProving%20the%20naysayers%20wrong%20became%20one%20of%20my%20main%20motivations%20after%20I%20enlisted.%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20that%20women%20can%20do%20just%20as%20well%2C%20if%20not%20better%2C%20than%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBattling%20self-doubt%20and%20growing%20as%20a%20leader%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221834%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jia%20Hui%20Ong.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65adef6843bb77284b9f0a37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOng%20was%20inspired%20by%20her%20father%2C%20who%20often%20told%20her%20about%20his%20experience%20as%20a%20commando%20during%20his%20national%20service%20days.%3Cp%3EJia%20Hui%20Ong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20leadership%20during%20my%20time%20with%20the%20SAF.%20After%20graduating%20as%20a%20sergeant%2C%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20a%20platoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20young%20leader%20was%20difficult%2C%20especially%20for%20someone%20still%20wrestling%20with%20self-doubt.%20I%20wasn't%20a%20natural%20leader.%20I%20made%20many%20mistakes%20during%20my%20training%2C%20which%20only%20fuelled%20my%20insecurities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20lost%20during%20my%20first%20field%20exercise%20as%20a%20section%20commander.%20I%20was%20embarrassed%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20blow%20to%20my%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20quite%20some%20time%20to%20get%20past%20this%20setback.%20However%2C%20I%20eventually%20found%20satisfaction%20as%20a%20leader%20when%20I%20improved%20my%20platoon's%20physical%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20train%20with%20them%20outside%20our%20working%20hours%2C%20using%20jerry%20cans%20as%20barbells%20and%20running%20with%20them.%20Seeing%20them%20perform%20better%20in%20their%20fitness%20assessments%20validated%20my%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELeaving%20my%20life%20in%20uniform%20wasn't%20easy%2C%20but%20it%20was%20necessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ong%20and%20her%20men.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a7a4dedcdb354a98581813%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOng%20(center)%20said%20her%20time%20with%20the%20SAF%20helped%20forge%20her%20identity%20and%20self-worth.%3Cp%3EJia%20Hui%20Ong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20SAF%20wasn't%20easy%20because%20so%20much%20of%20my%20identity%20and%20self-worth%20was%20built%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20considering%20other%20career%20opportunities%20during%20my%20fourth%20year%20of%20service.%20I%20also%20earned%20a%20degree%20in%20marketing%2C%20which%20allowed%20me%20to%20discover%20my%20creative%20side.%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20this%20interest%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20felt%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20innovation%20and%20initiative%20weren't%20appreciated%20in%20the%20army.%20People%20generally%20believe%20that%20if%20something%20isn't%20broken%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20fix%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20kind%20of%20thinking%20didn't%20resonate%20with%20me.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20a%20place%20with%20constant%20innovation%20and%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJoining%20the%20private%20sector%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20into%20the%20private%20sector%20wasn't%20a%20smooth%20ride.%20It%20was%20difficult%20to%20find%20a%20job%20because%20my%20military%20experience%20wasn't%20relevant%20to%20the%20corporate%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20to%20land%20an%20internship.%20But%20after%20my%20stint%2C%20a%20former%20SAF%20colleague%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20him%20at%20ST%20Engineering%2C%20a%20technology%20and%20engineering%20company%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20my%20responsibilities%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20product%20marketing%20and%20business%20development%20for%20defense%20simulation%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20ST%20Engineering%20felt%20very%20similar%20to%20my%20life%20in%20the%20SAF.%20I%20was%20engaging%20a%20lot%20with%20my%20ex-bosses%20and%20former%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20was%20a%20familiar%20environment%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20left%20the%20military%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20stagnate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20joined%20DBS%20Bank%2C%20where%20I%20managed%20their%20corporate%20credit%20cards.%20It%20was%20a%20full%20180-degree%20change%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20wasn't%20easy%2C%20but%20I%20could%20tap%20on%20some%20of%20the%20hard%20and%20soft%20skills%20I%20picked%20up%20from%20my%20SAF%20and%20ST%20Engineering%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELife%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20main%20difference%20I%20observed%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20versus%20the%20army%20was%20that%20everyone%20in%20the%20military%20appears%20to%20be%20working%20toward%20the%20same%20agenda%20and%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20everyone%20has%20their%20own%20agendas%20and%20personal%20goals.%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20be%20more%20discerning%20about%20whose%20agendas%20were%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20transitioning%20to%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20I%20also%20had%20to%20find%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20purpose%20in%20my%20work.%20When%20you%20are%20a%20soldier%2C%20your%20objective%20is%20set%20out%20for%20you.%20You%20put%20on%20the%20green%20uniform%2C%20and%20you%20serve%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20spending%20time%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20has%20helped%20me%20redefine%20my%20interests%20and%20strengths.%20It%20gave%20me%20a%20broader%20perspective%20of%20the%20world.%20That's%20something%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20learned%20if%20I%20had%20just%20stayed%20on%20with%20the%20SAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20say%20I%20have%20found%20my%20footing%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20I'm%20continuing%20to%20explore%2C%20and%20it%20works%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-army-for-private-sector-have-no-regrets-serving-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705880522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a779f943bb77284b9d9ac3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-army-for-private-sector-have-no-regrets-serving-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jia%20Hui%20Ong%20%2C%2026%2C%20served%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%20for%20five%20years%20before%20she%20made%20the%20transition%20to%20the%20private%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-army-for-private-sector-have-no-regrets-serving-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donetsk%3A%20Deadly%20blast%20hits%20market%20in%20Russia-held%20Ukraine%20city%2C%20officials%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705878864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FDF50%2Fproduction%2F_132386175_0f16b447095df4ec196e4025b8dd5617cef2b2ee0_228_6000_33752000x1125.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68047144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20rejects%20accusations%20from%20the%20region's%20Mos