20pass%20along%20with%20his%20or%20her%20Aadhaar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20khakhi-clad%20policemen%20are%20sprawled%20all%20over%20the%20place%2C%20while%20masons%2C%20artisans%20and%20both%20skilled%20and%20unskilled%20labour%20can%20be%20seen%20giving%20final%20touches%20to%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20the%20temple%20premises%2C%20which%20will%20be%20thrown%20open%20to%20people%20after%20the%20long%20high-profile%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20slated%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20entire%20ritual%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejajman%3C%2Fem%3E%20(master%20of%20ceremonies)%E2%80%99%20himself%2C%20the%20controversies%20that%20followed%20apparently%20led%20him%20to%20make%20room%20for%20a%20new%20jajman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20raised%20by%20top%20religious%20functionaries%20including%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20(the%20tallest%20priests%20under%20the%20Hindu%20order)%20were%20that%20the%20jajman%20had%20to%20necessarily%20be%20a%20Hindu%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20were%20required%20to%20live%20the%20life%20of%20a%20saint%20for%2011%20days%20before%20performing%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(consecration)%E2%80%99%20ceremony.%20Evidently%2C%20this%20criticism%20left%C2%A0%20Modi%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20opt%20out.%20His%20officials%20declared%20that%20since%20it%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20set%20aside%20all%20his%20official%20obligations%20for%2011%20days%2C%20hence%20a%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Anil%20Misra%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Usha%20were%20nominated%20as%20the%20new%20jajman%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20practicing%20homeopathic%20doctor%2C%20Misra%20was%20handpicked%20by%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20secretary%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20who%20has%20been%20handling%20the%20temple%20construction%20work%20ever%20since%20the%20trust%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2