erent%20caste%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Egarbh%20grah%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20temple%20was%20washed%20with%20water%20kept%20in%2081%20%3Cem%3Ekalsas%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(metal%20containers).%20This%20water%20is%20stated%20to%20have%20been%20drawn%20from%20different%20rivers%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20main%20%3Cem%3Epuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%2050%20minutes%2C%20after%20which%20he%20will%20address%20the%20guests%20and%20people%20of%20the%20country%20connected%20live%20through%20various%20TV%20networks%20and%20the%20digital%20media.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20will%20also%20meet%20the%20labourers%20and%20artisans%20engaged%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20Modi%20will%20spend%20four%20hours%20and%2045%20minutes%20in%20Ayodhya%20tomorrow.%20He%20will%20land%20at%20the%20newly%20built%20Ayodhya%20international%20airport%20at%2010%3A20%20am.%20From%20there%20he%20will%20take%20a%20short%20helicopter%20ride%20to%20the%20grounds%20of%20Saket%20Post%20Graduate%20College%2C%20close%20to%20the%20new%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20issues%20relating%20to%20the%20jajman%20have%20thus%20been%20resolved%2C%20controversy%20continues%20over%20the%20idol%20that%20will%20occupy%20the%20main%20garbh%20grah%20inside%20the%20temple.%20While%20the%20Trust%20and%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20have%20made%20it%20loud%20and%20clear%20that%20the%20new%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20be%20up%20for%20pran%20pratishtha%20at%20the%20main%20garbh%20grah%2C%20prominent%20local%20priests%20and%20even%20the%20highly%20revered%20Hindu%20Shankaracharyas%20strongly%20feel%20the%20the%20original%20idol%20of%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Lalla%E2%80%99%20merits%20a%20place%20in%20the%20garbh%20grah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20original%20idol%20that%20had%20appeared%20inside%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20then%20Babri%20Masjid%20on%20the%20night%20of%20December%2