ong%3EJalandhar%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWaiting%20for%20his%20skill%20test%20results%2C%2026-year-old%20Yogender%20Singh%20from%20Jind%20district%2C%20Haryana%2C%20is%20one%20among%20lakhs%20of%20candidates%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20Israel%20government%E2%80%99s%20recruitment%20programme%20for%20Indian%20construction%20workers%20at%20Maharshi%20Dayanand%20University%20(MDU)%2C%20Rohtak%2C%20Haryana.%20The%20recruitment%20was%20held%20between%20January%2016%20and%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Israel-Palestine%20is%20not%20a%20deterrent%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20find%20work%20and%20earn%20Rs%201.37%20lakh%20per%20month%20as%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20want%20to%20work%20but%20there%20are%20no%20jobs%20here.%20Even%20if%20you%20get%20some%20work%2C%20the%20salaries%20are%20too%20low%20to%20even%20manage%20basic%20expenses.%20What%20should%20a%20common%20man%20do%3F%20Had%20there%20been%20jobs%20in%20India%2C%20why%20would%20we%20think%20of%20going%20abroad%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20government%E2%80%99s%20recruitment%20was%20conducted%20by%20four%20different%20agencies%20including%20the%20Israel%20Population%20Immigration%20Border%20Authority%2C%20an%20Israeli%20government%20agency%20responsible%20for%20population%20registry%20and%20immigration%20topics%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Kaushal%20Rozgar%20Nigam%20Limited%20(HKRNL)%2C%20an%20employment%20website%20run%20by%20the%20Haryana%20government%2C%20the%20Foreign%20Cooperation%20Department%2C%20Haryana%20and%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogender%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20test%20as%20an%20iron%20welder%2C%20said%20that%20he%20learnt%20about%20this%20job%20opportunity%20from%20the%20HKRNL%20website%2C%20which%20keeps%20unemployed%20youth%20posted%20about%20job%20vacancies.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20options%20do%20we%20have%3F%20As%20an%20iron%20welder%2C%20either%20we%20come%20to%20Chandigarh%2C%20Punjab%20or%20Gurgaon%20for%20work%2C%20which%20is%20a%20costly%20affair.%20I%20hardly%20earn%20around%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20out%20of%20which%20by%20the%20end%20of%20month%20I%20am%20left%20with%20just%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20my%20pocket.%20How%20can%20someone%20survive%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20lamented%20the%20lost%20chance%20of%20joining%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20we%20had%20the%20option%20of%20joining%20the%20Army%20but%20even%20that%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20four-year%20Agniveer%20service.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20war%20in%20Israel%20is%20concerned%2C%20it%20does%20not%20matter%2C%20one%20can%20die%20anywhere.%20But%20at%20least%20in%20Israel%20we%20will%20get%20a%20good%20job%20and%20earn%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20the%20young%20men%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20skill%20test%20in%20Haryana%20had%20registered%20themselves%20with%20the%20HKRNL.%20However%2C%20there%20were%20many%20others%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20fleeced%20by%20fake%20travel%20agents%20charging%20Rs%201.5%20to%202%20lakh%20per%20person%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20test.%20Others%20or%20those%20who%20learnt%20about%20this%20opportunity%20through%20YouTube%20and%20other%20social%20media%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Israel%20is%20not%20part%20of%20e-migrate%2C%20a%20portal%20run%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20the%20workers%20will%20not%20be%20required%20to%20register%20themselves%20on%20it.%20The%20e-migrate%20portal%2C%20linked%20with%20the%20Passport%20Sewa%20Project%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20regulate%20overseas%20employment%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20less%20educated%20blue-collar%20workers%20or%20those%20moving%20to%20conflict%20zones%20or%20places%20without%20sufficient%20labour%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20Indian%20construction%20workers%20arose%20after%20Palestinian%20workers%20were%20banned%20from%20work%20in%20Israel%20after%20October%207.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Fisraeli-construction-sector-moves-to-replace-palestinian-employees-with-indian-workers%2F7338259.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVoice%20of%20America%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20construction%20sector%20had%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20allow%20companies%20to%20hire%20up%20to%20100%2C000%20workers%20from%20India%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20replace%2090%2C000%20Palestinians%20who%20were%20working%20in%20this%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fno-protections-for-migrant-workers-being-recruited-by-the-government-for-israel-labour-activists-to-move-court%2Farticle67740473.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20officials%20have%20questioned%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20send%20Indian%20workers%20as%20a%20replacement%20for%20Palestinian%20workers.%20The%20report%20mentioned%20that%20officials%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20India%20would%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20neutral%20party%20if%20this%20happened%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20targeting%20of%20about%20eight%20million%20Indians%20working%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20Gulf%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%20government%20issued%20advertisement%20in%20December%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20the%20HKRNL%20had%20issued%20an%20advertisement%20of%20job%20vacancies%20for%2010%2C000%20construction%20workers%20aged%20between%2025%20to%2045%20years%20in%20Israel%2C%20with%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20experience%20and%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201.37%20lakh%20per%20month%20(6%2C100%20new%20Israeli%20shekel).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20educational%20qualification%20for%20construction%20workers%20was%20a%20matriculation%20degree%20with%20three%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20concerned%20field.%20However%2C%20after%20witnessing%20a%20huge%20rush%20of%20applicants%2C%20the%20selection%20teams%20have%20made%20the%20recruitment%20open%20for%20everybody%20irrespective%20of%20their%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20required%20skills%20was%20industrialised%20building%20formwork%2C%20wood%20formwork%2C%20ceramic%20tiling%20of%20floors%20and%20walls%2C%20plastering%20work%20and%20iron%20bending%20with%20mandatory%20knowledge%20of%20reading%20construction%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Mason%20ka%20kaam%20hai%2C%20Rs%201.37%20lakh%20salary%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20MDU%20campus%2C%20Rohtak%2C%20one%20statement%20that%20could%20be%20heard%20from%20all%20applicants%20was%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMason%20ka%20kaam%2C%20hai%2C%201.37%20lakh%20salary%20%3C%2Fem%3E(It%E2%80%99s%20a%20mason%E2%80%99s%20job%20with%20a%20Rs%201.37%20lakh%20salary).%E2%80%99%20Helpless%20youth%20hoping%20to%20clear%20the%20interview%20were%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20good%20salary%20than%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurmeet%20Kashyap%20from%20Shahbad%20Markanda%20in%20Kurukshetra%20district%2C%20who%20applied%20for%20the%20mason%20skill%20test%2C%20was%20unfazed%20by%20the%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20what%20if%20war%20is%20going%20on%20in%20Israel%2C%20people%20are%20still%20staying%20there.%20Life%20is%20in%20God%E2%80%99s%20hands.%20At%20least%20in%20Israel%20we%20will%20have%20regular%20source%20of%20decent%20income.%20Here%20in%20India%2C%20leave%20alone%20a%20salary%2C%20people%20do%20not%20even%20pay%20us%20our%20daily%20wage%20on%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJatinder%20Kumar%2C%20a%20graduate%20from%20Mewat%2C%20Haryana%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20told%20that%20the%20workers%20will%20be%20kept%20in%20safe%20zones%20in%20Israel%20but%20I%20do%20not%20think%20so.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20damage%20in%20Israel%20because%20of%20the%20war.%20My%20father%20died%20and%20our%20financial%20condition%20is%20not%20good.%20%3Cem%3EGhar%20ki%20halat%20kharab%20hai%E2%80%A6paise%20ke%20liye%20ja%20rahe%20hai.%20Hamare%20liye%20zindagi%20maut%20ka%20sawal%20hai%2C%20kya%20karein%20%3C%2Fem%3E(We%20need%20the%20money%2C%20for%20us%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20life%20or%20death%20situation%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Haryana%20candidate%2C%20Kuldeep%20Singh%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20pass%20from%20Rewari%20district%2C%20also%20said%20that%20his%20financial%20condition%20was%20not%20stable.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20dependent%20on%20family%20farming.%20When%20there%20are%20no%20jobs%20here%2C%20obviously%20youth%20will%20rush%20to%20grab%20such%20an%20opportunity.%20But%20when%20we%20reached%20the%20university%2C%20we%20got%20to%20know%20that%20candidates%20from%20UP%20and%20Bihar%20were%20also%20there.%20Haryana%20candidates%20should%20be%20given%20priority%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20against%20the%20Haryana%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20former%20Haryana%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Karan%20Singh%20Dalal%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20state%20governor%20and%20sought%20his%20intervention%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20workers%20in%20war-torn%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20said%20that%20for%209.5%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Haryana%20failed%20to%20provide%20any%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20advertisement%20for%20jobs%20was%20issued%20when%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20were%20on%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20state%20and%20Central%20governments%20have%20not%20provided%20any%20protection%20to%20the%20applicants%20being%20sent%20to%20war%20affected%20Israel%2C%20which%20shows%20their%20lack%20of%20concern%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-Haryana%20applicants%20harassed%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20news%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20recruitment%20spread%2C%20many%20youths%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20states%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Punjab%20reached%20the%20university%2C%20exposing%20the%20scale%20of%20unemployment%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20following%20a%20lack%20of%20clarity%20about%20the%20rules%20of%20recruitment%2C%20non-Haryana%20applicants%20were%20left%20high%20and%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBraving%20the%20harsh%20cold%20like%20most%20applicants%2C%20Manish%2C%20who%20came%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20also%20clueless%20about%20the%20interview%20call%20and%20kept%20asking%20everybody%20about%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20through%20an%20agent%2C%20who%20demanded%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20skill%20test%20for%20Israel.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20not%20being%20treated%20at%20par%20with%20the%20natives%20of%20Haryana.%20I%20do%20not%20know%20if%20we%20will%20get%20a%20chance%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Sikar-based%20youth%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20said%20that%20he%20came%20for%20the%20Israeli%20recruitment%20through%20a%20state%20government%20agency.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20the%20Israel%20government%20was%20hiring%20masons%20at%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201.37%20lakh%20per%20month%2C%20I%20rushed%20to%20Rohtak.%20I%20am%20carrying%20my%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20passport%20and%20PAN%20card%20for%20proof%20but%20given%20the%20way%20the%20non-Haryana%20candidates%20are%20being%20treated%2C%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20that%20we%20will%20be%20considered%20for%20an%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20signed%20a%20three-year%20agreement%20with%20the%20Israeli%20government%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Facilitation%20of%20the%20Temporary%20Employment%20of%20Indian%20Workers%20in%20Specific%20Labour%20Market%20Sectors%20(Construction%20and%20Care-giving)%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20level%20of%20impatience%20of%20the%20applicants%20that%20despite%20being%20informed%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20will%20be%20holding%20a%20separate%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20construction%20workers%20in%20UP%20from%20January%2023%2C%20young%20people%20kept%20coming%20to%20Rohtak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bihar%20native%20from%20Betia%2C%20Ajay%20Paswan%2C%20who%20came%20along%20with%20a%20group%20of%20over%20a%20100%20people%2C%20said%20that%20an%20agent%20informed%20him%20about%20the%20job%20openings%20in%20Israel.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20an%20experienced%20worker.%20I%20have%20worked%20in%20Dubai%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20earlier.%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20life%20abroad%20but%20we%20are%20not%20being%20entertained.%20There%20is%20no%20clarity%20about%20the%20recruitment%20rules.%20While%20officials%20are%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20open%20for%20pan-India%20candidates%2C%20preference%20is%20being%20given%20to%20Haryana%20natives%20only%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20lamented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanesh%20Prasad%20Nishad%20from%20Varanasi%20also%20said%20that%20he%20came%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20this%20job.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20registered%20ourselves%20in%20UP%20and%20are%20eligible%20to%20apply.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20call%20us%20for%20an%20interview.%20The%20officials%20should%20give%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENSDC%20general%20counsel%20speaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20the%20media%20at%20MDU%2C%20Rohtak%20campus%2C%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Raina%2C%20group%20general%20counsel%20from%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20Delhi%2C%20who%20is%20handling%20the%20recruitment%20process%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20agreement%20was%20signed%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20the%20Israel%20government%2C%20after%20which%20the%20recruitment%20drive%20started%20in%20Haryana.%20The%20NSDC%20had%20written%20to%20different%20state%20agencies%20to%20mobilise%20youth%20to%20apply%20for%20these%20vacancies.%20The%20recruitment%20is%20free%20and%20fair.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20many%20applicants%E2%80%99%20claims%20that%20agents%20were%20charging%20money%20for%20the%20recruitment%2C%20Raina%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20authorised%20anybody%20to%20charge%20money%20from%20the%20applicants.%20Also%20contrary%20to%20the%20misunderstanding%2C%20the%20vacancies%20were%20open%20to%20people%20from%20entire%20country%20but%20because%20Haryana%20and%20UP%20took%20the%20initiative%2C%20we%20started%20the%20recruitment%20drive%20here.%20We%20will%20be%20holding%20a%20similar%20recruitment%20drive%20in%20UP%20from%20January%2023%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20queries%20on%20the%20safety%20of%20Indian%20construction%20workers%20in%20Israel%2C%20Raina%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20requested%20PIBA%20officials%20that%20our%20applicants%20will%20not%20be%20recruited%20in%20a%20war%20zone.%20Our%20talks%20are%20going%20on.%20Selected%20candidates%20would%20be%20reaching%20Israel%20within%2030%20days%20from%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20protesting%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20send%20workers%20to%20Israel%2C%20around%20ten%20major%20trade%20unions%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20Joint%20Platform%20of%20Central%20Trade%20Unions%20and%20Independent%20Federations%20in%20November%20last%20year%20had%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20reject%20the%20Israeli%20construction%20sector%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20replace%20Palestinian%20workers%20with%20Indian%20workers%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNothing%20could%20be%20more%20immoral%20and%20disastrous%20for%20India%20than%20the%20said%20%E2%80%98export%E2%80%99%20of%20workers%20to%20Israel.%20That%20India%20is%20even%20considering%20%E2%80%98exporting%E2%80%99%20workers%20shows%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20has%20dehumanised%20and%20commodified%20Indian%20workers.%20Such%20a%20step%20will%20amount%20to%20complicity%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20part%20with%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20genocidal%20war%20against%20Palestinians%20and%20will%20naturally%20have%20adverse%20implications%20for%20Indian%20workers%20in%20the%20entire%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705843846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21174919%2Frickshaw-2158447_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwould-rather-stay-here-but-there-are-no-jobs-say-those-at-israel-recruitment-drive-in-haryana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Exposing%20the%20extent%20of%20unemployment%20in%20India%2C%20young%20people%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20UP%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Punjab%20rushed%20to%20Rohtak%20to%20clear%20skill%20tests%20to%20work%20in%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwould-rather-stay-here-but-there-are-no-jobs-say-those-at-israel-recruitment-drive-in-haryana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Meets%20Protestors%2C%20Blows%20Kisses%20to%20BJP%20Supporters%20Raising%20Slogans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21185641%2FGEXZJsOWEAAun8w.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Assam%20leg%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20has%20been%20eventful%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20state%20government%20visibly%20unsettled%20by%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20start%20the%20Y